docs.lead_paragraph: ON BOARD PRESS BOAT With President Roosevelt, Montauk, L. I., Sept. 3.-Three fish fell to the rods of his party today as President Roosevelt spent the first day of his short vacation cruise off Montauk Point and along the surf shore of Eastern Long Island.
